data.description: Quiet home waiting on its new chapter! Great opportunity to turn this spacious 3 bed/1 bath into a charming home with huge living/dining rooms, a kitchen, bedrooms, bathrooms and bonus rooms ready for a gorgeous makeover.  Loft upstairs has tons of space and would make a wonderful den, rec area, office, play room, you name it!  Upper level is plumbed for a half bath.  Huge backyard for bbqs and outdoor fun with guests. Outdoor patio with front porch swing where you can enjoy breezy days and nights. Lots of great potential here! Selling As-Is. Property is part of an estate and in the process of being cleared out.
